    • save

      public void save() throws IOException
      The save method runs whenever the Save button is clicked. It attempts to add a new Appointment to the database, if the user inputs are valid. LAMBDA EXPRESSIONS: The OverlapInterface interface is implemented here, which checks for any overlapping Appointments with the provided start and end times.

      IOException
